latestIgtvVideos.title: Making my quarantine interesting with @kitchenxpresslimited
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
People close to me know how rarely I cook, I can say I don't like cooking much, unless it's a quick and easy dish I'll make it. during this Lockdown for the first time I'm trying my hands on @kitchenxpresslimited instant mix gulab jambun, they're so easy to make, I was so proud of myself for learning something new during this Lockdown!
If you give it a try do to tag me and @kitchenxpresslimited ! We will repost your stories! 
Have a sweet weekend!
